    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is an absolute stunner and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or dent in sight! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
