    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a museum-grade example of the high-revving S65 V8 platform. The naturally aspirated 4.0L powerplant remains in peak factory specification, delivering linear power through the 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. Critical maintenance items, including rod bearings and throttle actuators, have been proactively addressed with comprehensive service documentation. The chassis retains its original rigidity, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock that ensures surgical precision during high-lateral-G cornering. The Alpine White exterior is free of rock chips or paint depth inconsistencies, while the Novillo leather interior remains supple with zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key collector piece for the purist seeking the zenith of hydraulic-steering M-cars.",
      "price": 47800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 42500.0,
