    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating to ensure the paint remains free of swirls, rock chips, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and every switchgear provides a crisp, tactile response. Mechanically, this car is turn-key and flawless, supported by a comprehensive binder of every service record since mile one. It has never been driven in inclement weather, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. Sale includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and the unused factory tool kit. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that has been pampered rather than just driven.",
      "price": 42900.0,
