      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated VANOS system. The chassis remains structurally superior with a reinforced rear subframe and a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission feeding a variable M differential lock. Every body panel retains its original factory VIN tag, and the finish exhibits no imperfections or paint thickness deviations. The interior features Nappa leather with zero bolster wear, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. This is a collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
